    <p style="margin-bottom: 16px;">We built this tool because we believe clarity comes first. If you're at Level 1 and need to move to Level 2, we'd love to help &mdash; but we'll also tell you about Ruler Analytics, Attribution App, and a dozen other options. If you're at Level 3, you've outgrown us and we'll tell you that too.</p>
    <p style="color: var(--text);">Open scoring methodology. Vendor-neutral recommendations. No gate on your results. That's the deal.</p>
